 37 typedef struct _GHashTable  GHashTable;

 39 typedef gboolean  (*GHRFunc)  (gpointer  key,
 40                                gpointer  value,
 41                                gpointer  user_data);

 46 {
 47   /*< private >*/

 53   gpointer      dummy6;
 54 };
